---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">🆘 Help: What To Do If You're Screwed</h1>
  <p class="mb-6 text-lg">Missed half the semester? Behind on a course? Still possible to bounce back — here’s how.</p>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">⏳ Starting Late</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
      <li>Don’t try to finish the entire syllabus. Prioritize past year papers and scoring topics first.</li>
      <li>Use seniors' summaries or formula sheets to quickly grasp concepts.</li>
      <li>Focus on understanding solved questions instead of theory.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">📉 Low Midsem Scores?</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
      <li>Don’t give up — Endsems usually carry more weight and can save your grade.</li>
      <li>Ask TAs and professors directly what to focus on.</li>
      <li>Try group study — quick and productive if you’re short on time.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">🚀 Final Stretch</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
      <li>Use crash courses on YouTube (e.g., Neso Academy, Gate Smashers).</li>
      <li>Do not waste time making notes now. Revise directly from curated summaries.</li>
      <li>Study smart. Sleep well. Stay calm.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
